snippet: Brittney Griner had 24 points and 14 rebounds, and No. 3 Baylor beat No. 5 Notre Dame, 73-61, in South Bend, Ind., in a repeat of last season’s national championship game.
abstract: Baylor beats Notre Dame, 73-61, in women's college basketball; other scores noted in men's college basketball.

headline.main: Baylor Wins Rematch of Title Game
